SHELL

        Alt+F2                    Command dialog
        Alt+Space                 Switch keyboard layout
        Super+L                   Lock screen
        Ctrl+Alt+Delete           Log out, power off

APPLICATION

        Alt+Tab                   Switch application
        System+F10                Application menu

WINDOWS

        System+H                  Hide/minimize window
        System+Right/Left         Dock right/left half of workspace
        System+Up/Down            Toggle maximize
        Ctrl+Atl+Shift+[Up,Down]  Move window a workspace up/down
        Alt+Space                 Activate window menu
        Alt+F4                    Close window
        Alt+F7                    Move window
        Alt+F8                    Resize window
        Super+Shift+[left,Right]  Move windows to left/right monitor

WORKSPACE

        Super+Page[Up,Down]
        Ctrl+Alt+[Up,Down]        Switch workspace
        Super+Home                First workspace
        Super+End                 Last Workspace

TERMINAL

        Ctrl+Shift+N              New window
        Ctrl+Shift+Q              Close window
        Ctrl+Shift+C              Copy
        Ctrl+Shift+V              Paste
        Ctrl+[+,-,0]              Zoom in,out,normal

NAUTILUS

        Ctrl-N                    New window
        Ctrl-W                    Close window
        Ctrl-Q                    Close all windows
        F9                        Hide sidebar
        Ctrl+[1,2]                List/grid view
        Alt+[back,forward]        Go forward/back
        Alt+[up,down]             Go to parent/selected folder
        Ctrl+L                    Enter location
        Space                     Preview file
        Enter                     Open in default application
        Ctrl-F                    Search file
        Ctrl+Shift+N              Create folder
        F2                        Rename
        Ctrl-I                    File information
        Delete                    Move to trash
        Ctrl+[X,C,V]              Cut,Copy,Paste
        Ctrl+A                    Select all
        Ctrl+S                    Select by pattern
        Ctrl+H                    Toggle hidden files
        Ctrl+[+,-,0]              Zoom in, out, reset
